A quick note: <br>
<br>
When EQ 2 goes up, if there is a RP preferred server, I will be making an evil RP guild there. <br>
<br>
The core membership will be Teir'dal. Any race that can follow an evil deity though will be able to petition for membership. The guild will participate in large scale events that are both Rp and non Rp. An example of non Rp would be a classic raid type event. <br>
<br>
I will do my absolute best to assure that everyone in the guild is able to participate fully in Rp events. Some events of course will be scripted, however I will avoid having any one or two players trying to use the guild to grandstand and feed their egos. The guild will be as free style as possible. After all if tedious scripting is your desire, it would be better to rent a movie or watch a play. Basically I am aiming for the most dynamic and balanced organization possible. <br>
<br>
I come from three years in EQ. I started on the Karana server and later moved to Brell. I also have played on VZ, RZ and SZ. My principle EQ time however was invested on Brell. My characters included Xandriel T'sarijahl, Zressoth Freth, Mephala Freth, Xasojhet, and Vilothi V'drin. <br>
These were my major avatars, all were Teir'dal. Level range was 25- 52. <br>
<br>
In any case, if you are interested in forging a quality coalition in the up coming game, feel free to contact me, especially if I know you! My e mail is nrabelais@hotmail.com <br>
<br>
I am not posting the guild name and full details. I would like to secure the guild tag in game before I do such. I am working on a web page now as well. <br>
<br>
If you have a character background and are interested please post it in the tavern forum. Or send it to me.<br>
